## 21. Execution lifecycle

The lifecycle:

```text
1. load_package(package_dir)
2. validate package
3. create ExecutorBridge
4. create EvidenceWriter
5. create ContractSession
6. attach hook to host
7. host asks for current instruction
8. agent performs current step
9. agent submits result
10. session validates result
11. session executes via bridge
12. evidence is recorded
13. session advances
14. repeat until complete
```

Sequence:

```text
Agent Host
  -> Hook.get_current_prompt()
  -> Agent executes current instruction
  -> Agent calls submit_step_result(result)
  -> Hook.handle_tool_call()
  -> ContractSession.submit_result()
  -> ExecutorBridge.execute_step()
  -> EvidenceWriter.record()
  -> ContractSession.advance()
```

