## 25. Design decision summary

Final architecture:

```text
MOVA contract package
        ↓
loader + validator
        ↓
ContractSession
        ↓
current step instruction
        ↓
agent performs allowed work
        ↓
submit_step_result
        ↓
session validates
        ↓
ExecutorBridge executes according to binding
        ↓
EvidenceWriter records
        ↓
session advances
```

The agent is never allowed to own the business process.

The contract session owns the business process.

The executor bridge owns side effects.

Evidence owns audit.

Host adapters are thin and replaceable.

